    "rowsha": "DqDiHJZ7qQO2IzASOPHvn1VHBSXxX9ICEjbo8jchE/8=",
    "originContent": "> If bluetooth driver conflict with `gen4-mt7902` than please remove the bluetooth firmware so that it not interfere with this driver",
